OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGove names groups as he    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funveils extremism          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdefinition                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Michael Gove has named five groups he  
OL,6, said would be assessed against a new   
OL,7, government definition of extremism.    
OL,9,FThe communities secretary told MPs he  
OL,10,Fhad concerns about the "Islamist       
OL,11,Forientation" of three of the           
OL,12,Forganisations.                         
OL,14,FHe also named two groups he said       
OL,15,Fpromoted a "Neo-Nazi ideology".        
OL,17,FThe new extremism definition will apply
OL,18,Fto, but not criminalise, groups        
OL,19,Fpromoting an ideology based on         
OL,20,F"violence, hatred or intolerance".     
